      <title><![CDATA[Vim常用命令]]></title>
      <url>http://blog.linliner.com/2016/05/linux/shell/vim-commands-commons/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Vim工作模式"><a href="#Vim工作模式" class="headerlink" title="Vim工作模式"></a>Vim工作模式</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/linliner/blog.resources.1/master/2016/vim-mode.png" alt="Vim工作模式"></p>
<a id="more"></a>
<h2 id="插入命令"><a href="#插入命令" class="headerlink" title="插入命令"></a>插入命令</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">i    在光标前插入  </span><br><span class="line">a    在光标后插入  </span><br><span class="line">I    在当前行首插入  </span><br><span class="line">A    在当前行末尾插入  </span><br><span class="line">o    在光标当前行的下一行插入新行  </span><br><span class="line">O    在光标当前行的上一行插入新行  </span><br><span class="line">i——光标前， a——光标后， I——行首， A——行尾， o——插入下一行， O——插入上一行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="定位命令"><a href="#定位命令" class="headerlink" title="定位命令"></a>定位命令</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">:<span class="built_in">set</span> nu     显示行号  </span><br><span class="line">:<span class="built_in">set</span> nonu   取消行号  </span><br><span class="line">gg          到文本第一行  </span><br><span class="line">G           到文本最后一行  </span><br><span class="line">:n          到文本第n行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="删除命令"><a href="#删除命令" class="headerlink" title="删除命令"></a>删除命令</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x         删除光标处字符</span><br><span class="line">nx        删除光标后n个字符</span><br><span class="line">dd        删除光标所在行。</span><br><span class="line">ndd       删除n行。</span><br><span class="line">dG        删除光标所在行到末尾行的所有内容。</span><br><span class="line">D         删除光标处到行尾的内容。</span><br><span class="line">:n1,n2d   删除n1行到n2行，:189,211d  删除189到211行。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="替换和取消命令"><a href="#替换和取消命令" class="headerlink" title="替换和取消命令"></a>替换和取消命令</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">u        undo，取消上一步操作</span><br><span class="line">Ctrl+r   redo，返回到undo之前</span><br><span class="line">r        替换光标所在处的字符</span><br><span class="line">R        从光标所在处开始替换，按Esc结束替换</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="常用快捷键"><a href="#常用快捷键" class="headerlink" title="常用快捷键"></a>常用快捷键</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">shift</span> + zz      保存退出，与“:wq”作用相同</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="选中后的赋值粘贴"><a href="#选中后的赋值粘贴" class="headerlink" title="选中后的赋值粘贴"></a>选中后的赋值粘贴</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">v               进入字符可视模式，可逐个字符选中</span><br><span class="line">V 或 <span class="built_in">shift</span> + v  进入行可视模式，可每次选中一整行</span><br><span class="line">ctrl + v        进入块可视模式，可每次选中块状区域</span><br><span class="line">y               复制</span><br><span class="line">p               粘贴</span><br><span class="line">d               剪切</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    
